### ============================================
### PROVENI - BATCHES API TESTS
### ============================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### ============================================
### 1. AUTENTICAÇÃO
### ============================================

### 1.1 Login como MANAGER
# @name managerLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "marina@bonequinhos.com.br",
  "password": "marina123"
}

### 1.2 Login como SPECIALIST (para calcular CO2 e ver conformidade)
# @name specialistLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "specialist@proveni.com",
  "password": "specialist123"
}

### Cole os tokens abaixo após fazer login
@managerToken    = SEU_TOKEN_MANAGER_AQUI
@specialistToken = SEU_TOKEN_SPECIALIST_AQUI

### ============================================
### 2. POST /batches
###    Cria um novo lote (status inicial: DRAFT)
###    Roles: MANAGER, ADMIN
### ============================================

### 2.1 Criar lote completo
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "batchId": "LOT-2026-001",
  "productName": "Boneco de Plástico Reciclado",
  "productDescription": "Boneco articulado feito com plástico reciclado PCR",
  "quantity": 5000,
  "unit": "un"
}

### 2.2 Criar lote mínimo (só campos obrigatórios)
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "batchId": "LOT-2026-002",
  "productName": "Peça Injetada"
}

### 2.3 Criar outro lote para testes
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "batchId": "LOT-2026-003",
  "productName": "Embalagem Biodegradável",
  "productDescription": "Embalagem feita com material biodegradável",
  "quantity": 10000,
  "unit": "cx"
}

### 2.4 Testa batchId duplicado (deve retornar 500 - unique constraint)
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "batchId": "LOT-2026-001",
  "productName": "Lote Duplicado"
}

### 2.5 Body inválido - faltando campos obrigatórios (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 100
}

### ============================================
### 3. GET /batches
###    Lista todos os lotes da empresa do usuário logado
###    Roles: MANAGER, ADMIN
### ============================================

### 3.1 MANAGER lista lotes da sua empresa
GET {{baseUrl}}/batches
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 4. GET /batches/:batchId
###    Busca um lote específico pelo batchId
###    Roles: MANAGER, ADMIN
### ============================================

### 4.1 Buscar lote existente
GET {{baseUrl}}/batches/LOT-2026-001
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 4.2 Buscar lote inexistente (deve retornar 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/batches/LOT-INEXISTENTE
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 5. POST /batches/:batchId/calculate-co2
###    Calcula o CO2 total do lote somando os BatchSuppliers
###    Roles: MANAGER, ADMIN, SPECIALIST
### ============================================

### 5.1 MANAGER calcula CO2 do lote
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches/LOT-2026-001/calculate-co2
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 5.2 SPECIALIST calcula CO2 do lote
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches/LOT-2026-001/calculate-co2
Authorization: Bearer {{specialistToken}}

### 5.3 Calcular CO2 de lote inexistente (vai retornar totalCO2 = 0 pois não há BatchSuppliers)
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches/LOT-2026-002/calculate-co2
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 6. GET /batches/:batchId/compliance
###    Verifica conformidade do lote com a regra de CO2
###    Roles: MANAGER, ADMIN, SPECIALIST
### ============================================

### 6.1 MANAGER verifica conformidade (sem regra → sempre conforme)
GET {{baseUrl}}/batches/LOT-2026-001/compliance
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### 6.2 SPECIALIST verifica conformidade
GET {{baseUrl}}/batches/LOT-2026-001/compliance
Authorization: Bearer {{specialistToken}}

### 6.3 Conformidade de lote inexistente (deve retornar 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/batches/LOT-INEXISTENTE/compliance
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### ============================================
### 7. TESTES DE AUTORIZAÇÃO
### ============================================

### 7.1 SUPPLIER tenta criar lote (deve retornar 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_SUPPLIER_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "batchId": "LOT-INVALIDO",
  "productName": "Lote Não Permitido"
}

### 7.2 OPERATOR tenta criar lote (deve retornar 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/batches
Authorization: Bearer SEU_TOKEN_OPERATOR_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "batchId": "LOT-INVALIDO",
  "productName": "Lote Não Permitido"
}

### 7.3 Sem token (deve retornar 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/batches
